hotel_text.important_information:
Please note that the name of the credit card holder must be the same as the guest's name.

Please present the same credit card used to guarantee your booking when checking in / making payment at the hotel.

===
Guests booking nonrefundable rates are required to fill in the property's authorization form after the reservation is made. The form will be sent directly to guests's email and it must be sent back to the property's email within 24 hours once email is received.

===
Please note that breakfast is chargeable for children 6-11 years old. This charge is to be paid directly to the property.

policies.content: You can cancel free of charge until 3 days before arrival. You'll be charged the total price of the reservation if you cancel in the 3 days before arrival.

All children are welcome. 4 children under 6 years stay free of charge when using existing beds.
4 children from 6 to 12 year are charged  VND 1200000 per night when using existing beds.
One child under 2 years stays free of charge in a crib.
One child under 7 years is charged VND 1200000  per night in an extra bed.
The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1.
The maximum number of total guests in a room is 14.
The maximum number of cribs in a room is 1.
Any type of extra bed or crib is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management.
Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.
WiFi is available in the hotel rooms and is free of charge.
Free private parking is available  on site (reservation is not needed).
The property reserves the right to pre-authorize credit cards prior to arrival.
10 % VAT is included. 5 % Service charge is included. A City tax is not applicable.
